{"tid":2403372,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"時隔僅半年　IZ*ONE 3 月連開兩天線上演唱會！","createTime":"2021-02-11T05:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T05:54:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be7d484dd9914b45660f45a8cd596db430dde01f","tid":2403372,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_555d2bafa0643af2fdf1afe5a394c458/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-11/133648-896808.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_555d2bafa0643af2fdf1afe5a394c458%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-11%2F133648-896808.png&h=b989407c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n預定的合約期限即將到來，IZ*ONE 最近更積極地帶來各種活動，下個月又將在線上開唱！<br />\n<br />\nOff the Record 昨晚（10 日）閃電宣布 IZ*ONE 將於 3 月 13、14 兩日傍晚 5 點（韓國時間），舉行專場線上演唱會《ONE, THE STORY》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_6bf26952411641d719bfd24e3eb51fd5/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-11/133648-896807.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_6bf26952411641d719bfd24e3eb51fd5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-11%2F133648-896807.jpeg&h=0865f124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年 9 月，IZ*ONE 才剛舉行過線上演唱會《ONEIRIC THEATER》，不僅結合最新科技打造充滿臨場感的效果，也帶來許多前所未見的小組特別表演。<br />\n<br />\n在這次的《ONE, THE STORY》裡，IZ*ONE 也會帶來全新小組合作、表演沒公開過的歌曲⋯⋯等，16 日即可上各國的售票管道 InterPark Ticket、Ticket Pia、AXS 和 Mecimapro 預定門票。在演唱會來臨前，先來看看 IZ*ONE 送上的新年祝福吧！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s_-8ItlGcXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ds_-8ItlGcXw&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=0fa8e4cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s_-8ItlGcXw</a>"},{"pid":"791857434fa9e75b296804896a108f71a9686a47","tid":2403372,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"唔好係last con<img src=\"